preference.name: MELBChartStationTypes
preference.preference_description: Specifies the types of process areas used as stations on the X axis of the line balancing chart.If this preference is empty, Teamcenter uses the MEAllocationLevel preference value. If MEAllocationLevel is empty, the line balancing chart uses objects of the type Mfg0MEProcArea. Valid Values: Internal names of Mfg0MEProcArea or any of its subtypes.
